divs: Sighting DetailsI was delivering pizzas and I noticed two lights That were at an angle from each other they were pulsing red and going around eachother in circles I called mufon immediatly and was on the phone with a dispatcher in Florida as I was witnessing the ufos. I continued to observe for two minutes and eventually one of the craft flew away from the formation to the left and the other one stayed a bit longer and then went off to the right. My friend also saw the event from a different place. I was very excited during the event and was pulled over into a neighborhood where I flagged down a car with a family who also saw it briefly.
